# Hugo site

Forked from https://github.com/Yukuro/hugo-theme-shell, fixed some issues for recent version of hugo


 Change the config.toml located in the theme directory
 > For some reason it does not use the main folder config.toml, I do not care to find why now.
 
 *hugo server -D* to serve file locally
 
 *hugo* command to generate static files in public

 *podman build -t my-hugo-site .* tp build the image with podman
  
 *podman run -d -p 8080:80 my-hugo-site* to run the image with podman
